  "body": "# Highlights\r\n\r\nComplete TUI rewrite - dry has been ported from tcell/gizak-termui to Bubbletea v2, Bubbles v2, and Lipgloss v2. The new foundation brings better rendering, smoother scrolling, and a more maintainable codebase while keeping the same look and keybindings.\r\n\r\n## New features\r\n\r\n- Port dry TUI to Bubbletea v2 (#239)\r\n\r\n## Security\r\n\r\n- Update golang.org/x/crypto to v0.48.0 — fixes GO-2025-3487 (#241)\r\n\r\n## Maintenance\r\n\r\n- Upgrade Docker SDK from v27.5.1 to v28 (#244)\r\n- Automate releases with GoReleaser (#246)\r\n- Replace Dependabot with govulncheck + latest-deps testing (#240)\r\n- Update dependencies (#232)\r\n",
